result.name: choice-experiment-survey-data-flamborough-and-bempton-2014-2015
result.notes:
Raw data from the two choice experiment surveys at Flamborough and Bempton, 
East Yorkshire on the economic value of specific benefits of marine protected 
areas. Data is numerical and column heading is coded according to responses to 
the questions in the questionnaire. Some answers are categorical variables 
while some are continuous. Data has been anonymised. A code for the responses 
is included as a separate CSV file.
